data.value:
Selecta Fortified Milk is 100% fortified with vitamins for strong bones, body, and brain. It is fortified with "Vitagen" to build resistance and boost appetite of active kids. Selecta Fortified Filled Milk is Fortified with Vitamins A, D, B-Complex, Niacin and Calcium that comes from the trusted brand-Selecta.
type of milk: Filled milk
ideal for: individuals seeking a daily source of essential nutrients, particularly those looking to enhance their overall health and well-being.
Ingredients: Reconstituted Milk Powder (Skimmed Milk and Buttermilk), Refined Vegetable Oil (Mixture of Coconut and Corn Oil), Refined Sugar, Carrageenan (E407) Food Stabilizer, Mono-di- glycerides (E471) Emulsifier, Nature-Identical Flavor, Calcium, Vitamin B3, Maltodextrin, Vitamin A, Vitamin D3, Vitamin B1, Vitamin B12, Vitamin B6 and Vitamin B2 (E101).
Location: AllMart Grocery in Paranaque City, Metro Manila
Note: Selecta Fortified Milk is not a breastmilk substitute.
Serving Suggestion: Shake well. Serve chilled.
Storage Instructions: Once opened, keep refrigerated.
